[domain]
initially !droneReady
initially !airborne
inspectDrone causes droneReady
launchDrone causes airborne if droneReady
launchDrone costs 6

[queries]
airborne after inspectDrone, inspectDrone, launchDrone, launchDrone
inspectDrone, inspectDrone, launchDrone, launchDrone executable with exact cost 6
inspectDrone executable with exact cost 0
